textBeforeTable: WestlawNext Now Prints at Chicago-Kent You can now print from WestlawNext! WestlawNext Training If you are interested in additional WestlawNext training, check the schedule of trainings available on the Westlaw Lawschool Home page, under the Training tab. Both in-person and online training is available to you. If you have specific WestlawNext research questions, please feel free to stop by either of the computer labs in the library to ask a Westlaw Student Representative about WestlawNext. You will find us by looking for the "Westlaw Student Representative on Duty" sign. Opportunities to Earn Westlaw Rewards Points Westlaw encourages 1Ls (and every law student with a good research problem) to make an appointment with a Westlaw Student Representative, during their office hours.  Each student who makes (and keeps) an appointment will earn Westlaw Rewards Points.  Ask a Student Representative for details.   Weekly Study Aid Raffles Every week, the Westlaw Student Representatives at Chicago-Kent will be running a raffle for a study aid.  To win, stop by lab 900 to enter your name into the weekly drawing.  Each week’s winner will be notified via e-mail on Friday afternoon.  Even better, you may enter your name as many times as you wish.
